# Scripts and Tasks

Root scripts ([package.json](mdc:package.json)) run via Turbo:
- `pnpm dev`: runs dev for all
- `pnpm dev:web`: dev Nuxt on 3001 (HMR 3000)
- `pnpm dev:server`: dev Elysia server on `env.PORT` (default 3000)
- `pnpm build` / `pnpm start`: build/start all
- `pnpm check-types`: TS project references build
- DB: `pnpm db:push`, `pnpm db:generate`, `pnpm db:migrate`, `pnpm db:studio`
- Desktop: `pnpm desktop:dev`, `pnpm desktop:build`

Server app scripts ([apps/server/package.json](mdc:apps/server/package.json)) load `.env` from repo root.
Web app scripts ([apps/web/package.json](mdc:apps/web/package.json)) also load the root `.env`.